{"type": "article", "id": 2240, "title": "蔬果保鲜盖", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:38:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222300piEXDlcdofRtJ3SF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\tFood Huggers by <a href=\"http://foodhuggers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Adrienne McNicholas and Michelle Ivankovic</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t通常切开的蔬菜水果最容易从切面开始腐坏，设计师于是设计出了蔬果盖子，接触蔬果的地方由硅胶制成，可以完全贴合蔬果的切面，大大降低蔬果腐坏的速度，减少浪费。不论从持家角度还是道德角度，这都是个好设计，<a href=\"http://foodhuggers.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135154PY0gHmJVnNQ4Aybx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135155ZK5tzfMLCmcp9AQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135155cNFdtW9MRGY8DJXP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}